  ('Oklahoma Promise Scholarship', 'Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education', 'Full Tuition', '2026-06-15', 'Open to Oklahoma students in 8th-10th grade from families with incomes below $55,000; must take required high school courses, maintain a 2.5 GPA, and avoid substance abuse violations; covers tuition at Oklahoma public colleges', 'https://www.okhighered.org/okpromise/', false, true, 'Oklahoma, State-Specific, Financial Need, Low Income'),
