  ('American Farm Bureau Federation Scholarship', 'American Farm Bureau Federation', '10000', '2026-03-01', 'Open to undergraduate students from Farm Bureau member families pursuing degrees in agricultural, food, or fiber industry fields; based on agricultural background, academic achievement, and leadership; for students at two-year and four-year institutions', 'https://www.fb.org/educational-scholarship', true, false, 'Agriculture, Farming, Rural, Leadership'),
