  ('Scholarship America Dream Award', 'Scholarship America', '10000', '2026-12-15', 'Open to undergraduate students who have faced significant barriers to education including poverty, foster care, homelessness, or parental incarceration; demonstrates perseverance and resilience; renewable for up to three years with continued academic progress', 'https://scholarshipamerica.org/dreamaward/', true, true, 'Resilience, Underrepresented, Financial Need, Barrier');